I think @lamborghini really missed an opportunity here to call this color Lambo-greenie! The Huracán Tecnica LP-640 is the newest member of the #Lambo family and although, I think it’s a backwards step as far as styling, it’s a fantastic car to drive! The sounds it makes are glorious! 
.
.
#lamborghini #lamborghinihuracan #huracantecnica #v10 #italian #huracan #automotivephotography #carphotography #race #racetrack

.
.
#lamborghini #lamborghinihuracan #v10 #supercars #automotivephotography
The @lamborghini #Huracan #Tecnica is essentially a #Huracan #STO with a more livable interior and much more subtle styling. Most importantly, the STO’s 630HP is on tap, which means serious speed!

The @lamborghini #Huracan #Tecnica is a step forward in performance, but I think a step back as far as styling! Look at how good the #EVO and #STO look in comparison!
.
.
#lamborghini #lamborghinihuracan #lambo #supercar #hypercar #v10 #automotivephotography #carphotography

Big props to @darrenmartinphoto and @brandoodle for suffering the freezing #sunrise temperatures with the tops down! The @porsche #Turbo S Cab and @mercedesamg #SL63 are best enjoyed with the with the wind whipping through the cabin, even if that wind is frigid.🥶
If you come at the king, you best not miss! The @mercedesamg #SL63 is stylish, powerful, comfortable and fast… but the @porsche #Turbo S #cabriolet is a drop-top monster and really is the king cab!

There is no getting around the fact that all @porsche #Cabriolet are a little awkward looking with their tops down. The #Turbo additional rear spoiler only adds to the visual imbalance of the design. Luckily it makes up for it by being awesome!

It may not have won the @motortrend Performance Vehicle of The Year award or the comparison with @porsche #Turbo Cabriolet, but I still like the @mercedesbenzusa #SL63! The bright yellow throws me off a little bit, but I still think it’s a really good looking car!

Living life in the fast lane with these three speed demons! The BMW M5 CS, Cadillac CT5 Blackwing, and Mercedes-AMG GT63 are the ultimate sports sedans that make driving a thrilling experience. We pushed these beauties to their limits and enjoyed every second of it. Nothing beats a day of adrenaline, speed, and breathtaking views.

It has been almost 10 years since I shot these photos. By far the most epic road trip that I’ve ever photographed was a 10-day grand tour of Alberta in a @nissanusa #GTR for @automobilemag ! I have actually shared most of these photos on Instagram before, but like I said, it was 10 years ago, so it might as well have never happened! Enjoy! 
-
#nissangtr #nissan @nissan #godzilla #alberta #tourismalberta @tourismalberta #canada #ohcanada #supercar #turbo

Almost done with this trip down memory lane. Looking through these again has rekindled my desire to return and to explore more of this epic area. @nissanusa #GTR in #Alberta
.
#nissan #nissangtr #r35 #r35gtr #travel #landscape #supercar #turbo #godzilla  @motortrend

Ok, last one of the @nissanusa #GTR in #Alberta. This is one of my favorites based on how it was shot! Car-to-Car or #Rollers are action photos taken from one moving car, back at another moving car. This is Boat-to-Car! Myself and a videographer were sitting in a tiny motorboat desperately trying to match the GTR’s speed. 

Other variations of Car-to-Car (Car2Car) that I have done are as follows: Car2Car, Car2Boat, Boat2Boat, Plane2Plane, Car2Dog, Car2Cow, Car2Horse, Car2Motorcycle, Car2Person
.
